qDef.qDef:
Pick(
[%SynCostLossMatrixXDimensionsWithTotals],
	//Direct Material
	Pick(
    [%SynCostLossMatrixYDimensionsWithTotalCosts]
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Material_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Setup_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Material_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Setup_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Direct_Material_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_CLM_Total_Losses_Cost)),'#0.00%')
    ,Num($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_MaterialCost_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Direct_Material_CM_YTD))/$(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_MaterialCost_CM_YTD),'#0.00%') 
    ),
    
    
    //Conversion Cost
    Pick(
    [%SynCostLossMatrixYDimensionsWithTotalCosts] 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Speed_Losses_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Speed_Losses_CM_YTD) + 
     $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD) + 
     $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) +
     $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD) +
     $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD) + 
     $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Conversion_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_CLM_Total_Losses_Cost)),'#0.00%')
    ,Num($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_ConversionCost_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Conversion_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_ConversionCost_CM_YTD)),'#0.00%')
    ),
    
    //Maintenance Cost
    Pick(
    [%SynCostLossMatrixYDimensionsWithTotalCosts]
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_Maintenance_Labour_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(V_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_NSI_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_Maintenance_Labour_CM_YTD) +
     $(V_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_NSI_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Maintenance_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_CLM_Total_Losses_Cost)),'#0.00%')
    ,Num($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_MaintenanceCost_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Maintenance_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_MaintenanceCost_CM_YTD)),'#0.00%')
    ),
    
    //Operational Cost
    Pick(
    [%SynCostLossMatrixYDimensionsWithTotalCosts]
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Material_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Speed_Losses_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Setup_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_Maintenance_Labour_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(V_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_NSI_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Material_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Setup_Waste_CM_YTD)
    +$(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Speed_Losses_CM_YTD) +  $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD) +  $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD) +
     $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD) +  $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD) 
    +$(v_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_Maintenance_Labour_CM_YTD) + $(V_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_NSI_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Direct_Conversion_Maintenance_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_CLM_Total_Losses_Cost)),'#0.00%')
    ,Num($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_Operational_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Direct_Conversion_Maintenance_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_Operational_CM_YTD)),'#0.00%')
	)
    ,
    
    //Depreciation Cost
    Pick(
    [%SynCostLossMatrixYDimensionsWithTotalCosts]
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Speed_Losses_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Speed_Losses_CM_YTD) + 
     $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD) + 
     $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) +
     $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD) +
     $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD) + 
     $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Depreciation_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_CLM_Total_Losses_Cost)),'#0.00%')
    ,Num($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_DepreciationCost_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Depreciation_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_DepreciationCost_CM_YTD)),'#0.00%')
    ),
    
    //Sub Total
    Pick(
    [%SynCostLossMatrixYDimensionsWithTotalCosts]
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Material_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Speed_Losses_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Speed_Losses_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Setup_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_Maintenance_Labour_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(V_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_NSI_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Material_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Direct_Material_Cost_Setup_Waste_CM_YTD)
    +$(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Speed_Losses_CM_YTD) +  $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD) +  $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD) +
     $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD) +  $(v_CLM_Conversion_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD) 
    +$(v_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_Maintenance_Labour_CM_YTD) + $(V_CLM_Maintenance_Cost_NSI_CM_YTD)
    +$(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Speed_Losses_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD) +  $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) + $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD) +
     $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD) +  $(v_CLM_Depreciation_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Direct_Conversion_Maint_Depr_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_CLM_Total_Losses_Cost)),'#0.00%')
    ,Num($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_Operational_CM_YTD) +$(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_DepreciationCost_CM_YTD)  ,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Direct_Conversion_Maint_Depr_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_Operational_CM_YTD) +$(v_Production_Costing_Cost_Amount_Real_DepreciationCost_CM_YTD)),'#0.00%')
     ),
    
    //Opportunity Cost
    Pick(
    [%SynCostLossMatrixYDimensionsWithTotalCosts]
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Material_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Speed_Loss_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Setup_Waste_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num($(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Material_Waste_CM_YTD) + 
     $(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Speed_Loss_CM_YTD) + 
     $(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Production_DT_CM_YTD) +
     $(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Production_Waste_CM_YTD) +
     $(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Setup_DT_CM_YTD) + 
     $(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Setup_Waste_CM_YTD) + 
     $(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Maintenance_DT_CM_YTD) +
     $(v_CLM_Opportunity_Cost_Other_DT_CM_YTD),'#,##0') 
    ,Num(($(v_CLM_Total_Opportunity_Cost_CM_YTD)) / ($(v_CLM_Total_Losses_Cost)),'#0.00%')
    ,Num(0,'#,##0') 
    ,Num(0,'#0.00%')
    ),
    
       //Total
    $(v_CLM_Total_Cost_Synth_Headers),
	
	   // % of Total
	$(v_CLM_Perc_of_Total_Synth_Headers)
    
)
